                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040912-54-defend620 t18040912-54-punish322"></join>
               Whipped in the jail and discharged
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Chambre.</p>
